snippet: Lexi Thompson picked up five shots in four holes in a five-under-par 66 to claim a share of the lead with Mi Hyang Lee in the opening round.
abstract: Lexi Thompson and Mi Hyang Lee share first round lead at Evian Championship golf tournament.
